        <text>
            <body>  <p>Ego <persName key="d1e11498" xml:id="d1e129803">Matildis, comitissa
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324459" xml:id="d1e129805" corresp="Grignon (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Grinionis</placeName>
                        </persName>, notum facio presentibus et futuris quod <app>
                            <lem wit="#A">Rainerius</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#B">Renerius</rdg>
                        </app> de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324356" xml:id="d1e129814" corresp="Seigny (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">
                            <foreign>
                                <app>
                                    <lem wit="#A">Segne</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#B">Saigne</rdg>
                                </app>
                            </foreign>
                        </placeName>
                        <lb n="2" /> et <persName key="d1e11505" xml:id="d1e129823">Petrus de
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325042" xml:id="d1e129825" corresp="Vallibus">Vallibus</placeName>, frater ejus</persName>, in perpetuam
                        elemosinam ecclesie Fonteneti dederunt<note> dederunt
                            <hi rend="italic" xml:space="preserve">écrit avant </hi>de censu de
                            Estormer <hi rend="italic">avec signe de correction A</hi>,
                            <hi rend="italic" xml:space="preserve">placé devant </hi>in perpetuam
                            elemosinam B.</note>
                        <app>
                            <lem wit="#A">quindecim</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#B">xv</rdg>
                        </app> soli<lb n="3" break="no" />dos censuales quos debebant eis monachi
                            <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e129850" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> de
                        censu de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324449" xml:id="d1e129853" corresp="Étormay (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">
                            <foreign>Estormer</foreign>
                        </placeName>. <lb n="4" /> Hoc laudavit <persName key="d1e11511" xml:id="d1e129859">Ansericus, filius <app>
                                <lem wit="#A">Rainerii</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B">Renerii</rdg>
                            </app>
                        </persName> et ceteri pueri ejus, et <persName key="d1e11517" xml:id="d1e129868">Adelina, uxor Petri de Va<lb n="5" break="no" />llibus</persName>, coram his testibus, <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324623" xml:id="d1e129873" corresp="Eudes, archiprêtre de Touillon (1173-1200)">Odone archipresbitero <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324370" xml:id="d1e129875" corresp="Touillon (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Tullionis</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e11523" xml:id="d1e129878">Humberto de
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324962" xml:id="d1e129880" corresp="Monte Sancti Johannis">Monte Sancti
                                Johannis</placeName>, <lb n="6" /> monacho Fonteneti</persName>,
                            <persName key="d1e11529" xml:id="d1e129886">
                            <app>
                                <lem wit="#A">Olivero</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B">Oliverio</rdg>
                            </app> de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324459" xml:id="d1e129893" corresp="Grignon (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Grinione</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e11535" xml:id="d1e129896">Oberto, fratre
                            jamdicte <app>
                                <lem wit="#A">Andeline</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B">Adeline</rdg>
                            </app>
                        </persName>. Actum est hoc <lb n="7" /> in <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324453" xml:id="d1e129907" corresp="Fontenay (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">capitulo Fonteneti</placeName>, anno ab incarnatione
                        Domini <num>
                            <app>
                                <lem wit="#A">millesimo</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B">m°</rdg>
                            </app> c° xc° <app>
                                <lem wit="#A">sexto</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B">vi°</rdg>
                            </app>
                        </num>. Ut autem hoc ratum habeatur in posterum, sigilli mei munimine
                        roboravi.</p>
                
